== Spell Mechanics ==

=== Damage Formula ===

<pre>
Base Damage = Power × (Magic / 4 + 8)
Resistance = 1.0 - (Target Resist / 100)
Final = Base × Resistance × Element Modifier
</pre>

=== Success Rate (Status Spells) ===

<pre>
Hit Rate = Accuracy + (Caster Magic - Target Wisdom) / 2
</pre>

=== MP Costs ===

All spells have fixed MP costs. No spell costs more than 50 MP.

== Spell Data Structure ==

Spells are stored in ROM at $15:8000:

<pre>
struct Spell {
    uint8   mp_cost;        // $00: MP cost
    uint8   power;          // $01: Base power
    uint8   accuracy;       // $02: Hit rate
    uint8   element;        // $03: Element type
    uint8   target_type;    // $04: Target mode
    uint8   effect_type;    // $05: Effect category
    uint8   status_effect;  // $06: Status to apply
    uint8   animation;      // $07: Animation ID
    uint8   school;         // $08: White/Black/Wizard
    uint8   level_req;      // $09: Required level
    uint8   reserved[6];    // $0A-$0F: Reserved
}
</pre>

